This folder contains the following files:
- ASWING_test_output: text-like ASWING output, used to pass data from ASWING to WingLoop
- matlab_test_controller.m: very simple matlab controller used with WingLoop  
- simulink_test_controller.slx: very simple simulink controller used with WingLoop
- python_test_controller.py: very simple matlab controller used with WingLoop

DA COMPLETARE E RIFARE l'APPLICAZIONE (files sono stati cambiati)
E mettere dentro WingLoop la ASWING Director (non update il contenuto di 10_..)
